OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771879288
OL,3,CFootballer Leny Yoro given driving ban
OL,4,Cfor 72mph speeding offence outside
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FManchester United footballer Leny Yoro
OL,8,Fhas been handed a six-month driving
OL,9,Fban after driving his Porsche at more
OL,10,Fthan 70mph as it passed a school.
OL,12,FThe 20-year-old centre back was fined
OL,13,Fa total of #1,052 after his #170,000
OL,14,FPorsche Cayenne was clocked at 72mph
OL,15,Fby a camera in the Manchester suburb
OL,16,Fof Withington in August 2025.
OL,18,FCourt papers reveal Yoro was driving
OL,19,Fat nearly two-and-a-half times the
OL,20,F30mph speed limit at the time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
