OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771879288
OL,3,CFootballer Leny Yoro given driving ban
OL,4,Cfor 72mph speeding offence outside
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FLawyers for the French defender issued
OL,8,Fan apology on his behalf, insisting
OL,9,Fthat the road was clear at the time
OL,10,Fand Yoro was "rushing to take a friend
OL,11,Fto the railway station".
OL,13,FYoro was hit with a six-month driving
OL,14,Fban, a #666 fine, and was ordered to
OL,15,Fpay #120 in costs and a #266 victim
OL,16,Fsurcharge, at Crewe Magistrates' Court
OL,17,Fon 21 February.
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771879288
OL,3,CFootballer Leny Yoro given driving ban
OL,4,Cfor 72mph speeding offence outside
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FLisa Nevitt, Yoro's lawyer, wrote to
OL,8,Fthe court highlighting the
OL,9,Ffootballer's "prompt guilty plea" and
OL,10,Fsetting out that he "would not seek to
OL,11,Fargue that he should not be
OL,12,Fdisqualified".
OL,14,F"He is not liable to a totting up
OL,15,Fdisqualification but understands
OL,16,Fbecause of the speed involved that it
OL,17,Fis highly likely the court will impose
OL,18,Fa disqualification rather than penalty
OL,19,Fpoints," she wrote.
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@aO]rD@UOUtD@MO]vD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
