OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771879288
OL,3,CFootballer Leny Yoro given driving ban
OL,4,Cfor 72mph speeding offence outside
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,F"Our client would like to take this
OL,8,Fopportunity to apologise for the
OL,9,Fincident which came about as he was
OL,10,Frushing to take a friend to the
OL,11,Frailway station.
OL,13,F"Our client further states that he
OL,14,Fbelieves where the speeding took place
OL,15,Fwas at a point where the road was
OL,16,Fbroad and there was little prospect of
OL,17,Fbeing any contact with any vulnerable
OL,18,Froad users such as pedestrians."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771879288
OL,3,CFootballer Leny Yoro given driving ban
OL,4,Cfor 72mph speeding offence outside
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FThe incident happened at just after
OL,8,F4pm on 28 August 2025, when Yoro was
OL,9,Fdriving the Porsche Cayenne GTS along
OL,10,FMauldeth Road West in Withington.
OL,12,FThe stretch of road is lined in places
OL,13,Fwith homes, as well as a secondary
OL,14,Fschool and a sports club.
OL,16,FThe force said in court documents that
OL,17,Fletters asking for information went
OL,18,Funanswered when sent to Yoro's
OL,19,FCheshire home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
