OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771879288
OL,3,CFootballer Leny Yoro given driving ban
OL,4,Cfor 72mph speeding offence outside
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FYoro was not required to appear in
OL,8,Fcourt, as his case was dealt with
OL,9,Fbehind closed doors in the single
OL,10,Fjustice procedure, allowing magistrate
OL,11,FSunjeep Bhalla to convict and sentence
OL,12,Fthe star based on written evidence
OL,13,Falone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
